                            <comment id="58541" author="spitzcor" created="Wed, 15 May 2013 05:07:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;FYI: I opened &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3320&quot; title=&quot;Single 2.6-rhel6.series for lustre kernel patches whereas ldiskfs kernel patches support multiple 2.6-rhel&amp;#39;s&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3320&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3320&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; to track the way that change #5952 broke builds on CentOS 6.3 servers.  It would have been nice if the changes were made a la the recent ldiskfs kernel patch series where both 6.3 and 6.4 servers are simultaneously supported in-tree.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="56188" author="pjones" created="Fri, 12 Apr 2013 05:38:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Landed for 2.4&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="55914" author="jlevi" created="Tue, 9 Apr 2013 18:13:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,5952&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,5952&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="53186" author="simmonsja" created="Thu, 28 Feb 2013 14:38:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;You will need patch &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,4991&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,4991&lt;/a&gt; as well.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="52830" author="simmonsja" created="Thu, 21 Feb 2013 14:43:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Also I see from the patch for b2_1 that you ran into the issue of the ext4_ext_pblock renaming. I have a patch for that at &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,5001&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,5001&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="52829" author="simmonsja" created="Thu, 21 Feb 2013 14:40:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;ldiskfs patches are here &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,4804&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,4804&lt;/a&gt; from &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2473&quot; title=&quot;ldiskfs RHEL6.4 support&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-2473&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-2473&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
